# BuddyBot project rules

- Do NOT read files in /build, /.gradle, /app/build, or /node_modules directories
- Do NOT read more than 3 files per task unless I explicitly ask you to
- Always show me a diff preview before applying any changes
- Only edit the exact file and line numbers I specify
- Do not refactor, rename, or reorganise any code I have not mentioned
- When a task is complete, stop. Do not look for more things to fix.
- If context usage reaches 70%, summarise and start a new task